iness_summary":"Purity Flexpack Limited manufactures and sells flexible packaging materials in India and internationally. The company offers printed/unprinted roll stocks comprising multi-layer adhesive, co-extrusion, stick pack, and paper-based lamination rolls; cold seal packaging, wrap around BOPP label, and HFFS/VFFS/flow wrap rolls; and lidding laminations. It also provides standard pouches, such as central seal/pillow, side gusset central seal, three side seal, Doy pack/stand up, quad seal, and Penta seal pouches; speciality application pouches, including retort, spouted, de-gassing valve, flat-bottom, 4 side flat box, vacuum, and shaped pouches, as well as heavy duty bags; shrink sleeves; and add-ons comprising tear notches, child resistant zippers, D cut/hang holes, laser scoring, pocket zippers, plastic/tread handles, registered matt/gloss prints, Velcro zippers, register window metalized/die-cut windows, security ink printing, and holographic laminates. In addition, the company serves various sectors, such as frozen food and vacuum, powder, liquid, instant noodle, agriculture, chemical, snack food, and retort product industries, as well as the bread and confectionery, and pharmaceutical industries. The company was incorporated in 1988 and is based in Halol, India."}}